\id 3JN - Guhu-Samane NT [ghs] -Papua New Guinea 1975 (DBL 2014) 
\h 3 Dzohane 
\toc1 3 Dzohane Noho Dzaira Pepa Ipina 
\toc2 3 Dzohane 
\toc3 3 Dzoh 
\mt1 3 DZOHANE  
\mt2 NOHO DZAIRA PEPA IPINA  
\ili Dzohane Dzebeteo qeeteta  
\ili Epeso, Asia Gattiqa  
\ili Tii 80  
\ib  
\ili Gaidzo, Sinabidza Abi  
\ili Nagapa tee  
\ili Ttoka ma Haba tee  
\c 1  
\s1 PASARAHO NOO  
\m
\v 1 Dzoobe Dzaira:  
\p Ana Dzohane Sinabidzaho sooparai Gaidzo niiho quba noorake qeesuqi meenipamu niiho quba dzasa eete.  
\v 2 Ana nookami niiho qupa khatai isanatoraihe, niiho sama ma gama oho qesa ohongahonga naatorareiqi ana Ohonga pupu hiirorai.   
\p
\v 3 Oi dzairamane qesai baaqi niiho isere mee hiireqi hee, Nii tete meenomake iihoraiqi hiireta.  
\v 4 Oonita erai teeho quba bahe, naho khameto qesama nikei tete mee iihoraiho isereke ana nookama ota naho qupa qidzanipamu naataridzoni.   
\s1 GAIDZO KOKORA QIDZA EETOTAHO HASA HIIRETA  
\p
\v 5-6 Dzaira name, sinabidza abi ika ma ika neta baami nii dzasa quba nokoho kokora bagenoma eetemi nokoi oko ma boto tupu nanahota oho isere mootorai. Oonita nii Ohongake qupadzomaqi nokoke roherohe eetemi baurata tuumoraqu oi qidza.   
\p
\v 7 Oi nokoi nagapa nokome qaateqi baurata tuumaqi teqaha raaba abihota soomoraidzaranita qupadzomare.  
\v 8 Napai abi oonomake too teeteqi sinabidzaho ttaiqanipamu naataridzo, dzoobe.   
\s1 TTIOREPE MA TEMETERIHO ISERE  
\p
\v 9-10 Qate ana oko ma boto tupuho quba gee teeke qeetetahe, Ttiorepe noi noomae bosa qobaqoba naatareiqi beedzae eete nanake kuimorai. Ma oi keke bahe sinabidza abi qesai ota biranatemi noi nokoke kuibiremi qesai baura eetareimi noi nokoke qaga hiireqi tuputa qirutomorai. Oho quba ana naamae ota biranateqake baura nohoho khooba sigumaqa oke pobitakoi. Noi nanaho qoreke hiireqi noo arinoma hiirorai.   
\p
\v 11 Dzaira name, qanga eetorai abi noi Ohonga moo pobitaama, qate, baura qidza eetorai noio Ohongaho nena. Oonita tete qanga bahe qidzaqake nii gesina naate qaarareiqi ana niike qupanomaisubi.   
\p
\v 12 Qate abi Samane Temeterioho isere mootoqi hee, noi baura mee keke eetorai. Oho qesa nanamae noho isere qidza mootomi nanaho isere meenoma naatoraike nii gesina.   
\s1 AIPOHO NOO  
\p
\v 13 Maaqa noo samaneke ana niiho quba qeetarorihe qidzoke poso ma eehoma oke qeete soubidzaqu.  
\v 14-15 Oonihe anai ao niiho toro biranate naka penga teenaite noo hiibareiqi qupadzome. Qate naho qesamane erana oorai nokoi niiho quba dzoobe hiire. Ma nii paha nanaho dzairamane temu ma temu gama ota dzoobe hiibare.  
\q1 Oionita aipoo  
\q1 Anai Dzohane   